								        tell their story effectively, and maximise donations.
			</p>

			<div class="hero__actions">
				<a href="#get-started" class="hero__btn hero__btn--primary">Get Started</a>
				<a href="#learn-more" class="hero__btn hero__btn--secondary">Learn More</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="hero__visual">
